    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain benefits from a recently serviced M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its aluminum five-link rear suspension and EDC (Electronic Damper Control) to provide exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Maintenance is up to date, including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, making this a mechanically sound specimen for the discerning driver. The exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, but the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
