      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only the expected minor imperfections from careful road use. Step inside to find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather seating and a fully functional dashboard where every button and feature operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is robust; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a comfortable, quiet ride. Recent service records are available, and the tires have plenty of life left. It\u2019s a turn-key car that perfectly bridges the gap between a reliable daily driver and a pride-of-ownership cruiser.",
